Comment: I think it is a simple problem with potential for Clash of code

Goal
* Please delete "Just as the title says".

* Please change "characters" to "letters".

* Please change "next to" to "come after".

Input
* Please add "[[l]]" after "One alphabet letter".

* Please delete 'If the given letter is the last of the alphabet then output "Here's the end"'.

Output
* Please rewrite as follows:

If [[l]] is not the last letter of the English alphabet, output all the subsequent letters in the same case, one per line.

If [[l]] is the last letter of the alphabet, output {{Here's the end}}.

Constraints
* Please rewrite as follows:

[[l]] is always a valid single letter from the English alphabet ({{A}}-{{Z}} or {{a}}-{{z}}).

Stub generator
* Please add a write statement, e.g. "write answer".

Thanks.
